    align:rationale "The descriptions are almost identical, focusing on data used for independent AI system evaluation before deployment. The lexical similarity is high (0.833). While 'Data Testing' (AIDOC) sounds like an *activity*, and 'TestingData' (dpv-aiact) a *thing* (data itself), the core meaning is equivalent in this context – they refer to the same concept."^^xsd:string ;
